        <abstract> 
<p>Sends CD a copy of his memoir on the fenland [<hi rend="italic">Geology of the fenland</hi> (1877)].</p> 
            <p>Outlines the results of his recent researches into the geological history of man, the development of Palaeolithic culture, the occurrence of Palaeolithic remains in the boulder-clays of eastern England, and their relation to glacial and inter-glacial periods.</p>
        </abstract>
